By syncing your text editor, you agree to share information from your text editor to enable us to make learning recommendations based on your programming activity. Pluralsight gathers the time of day and duration of each coding session, the language(s) you use to code, and the libraries in your code. We do not copy your source code. If you do not want to share this data with Pluralsight, please do not sync your text editor. Use of this service and all data gathered is subject to Pluralsight's Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.
